=== Etymology ===
From Greek meaning "longhaired star", due to the long "tail" of a comet.

===Noun===
'''comet'''

#A [[celestial body]] consisting mainly of [[ice]], [[dust]] and [[gas]] in a (usually very [[eccentric]]) [[orbit]] around the [[Sun]] and having a "tail" of melted matter blown away from it by the [[solar wind]] when it is close to the Sun.

